to.networld.scrawler.foaf
Class Agent

java.lang.Object
  to.networld.scrawler.common.RDFEntity
      to.networld.scrawler.foaf.Agent
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFOAFAgent
public class Agent
extends RDFEntity
implements IFOAFAgent

Agent entity that handles person. The selfURI is a FOAF file that could be queried with SPARQL. The class don't search the friend automatically. The friends are the only information that are stored. All other information are gained ad-hoc.

Author:
Alex Oberhauser
